,45,11,21,32,1,1,2,86,97,183,2,2,4,89,100,189,'2025-08-29 14:43:50','2025-11-19 01:08:13'),(19,33,1,1,1,'2025-11-14 00:00:00','2025-11-30 00:00:00','ongoing','<p>Health Monitoring: The Silver Monitor is a smartwatch designed for seniors, offering continuous health monitoring and safety features. It tracks vital stats like blood pressure, heart rate, and temperature, and includes features like fall detection and activity tracking. This system aims to enhance the well-being of seniors by providing real-time health insights and support</p>','<p>Silver Price Monitoring: The Silver Price is tracked in real-time, with current prices available from various sources. This is important for investors and those interested in the market dynamics of silver.&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Both aspects of silver monitoring are crucial for individuals and businesses involved in health and financial sectors.</span></p>','<p>Futures trading at 0.7¢ discount suggests strong physical demand or supply constraints making immediate delivery more valuable than future delivery.</p><div><br></div>',NULL,3,4,7,4,4,8,5,5,10,3,4,7,1,1,2,13,15,28,1,1,2,15,17,32,'2025-11-06 02:16:38','2025-11-06 02:16:38'),(20,33,2,2,1,'2025-11-01 00:00:00','2026-02-08 00:00:00','ongoing','<p>a</p>','<p>b</p>','<p>v<u>c</u></p>',NULL,23,33,56,5,4,9,3,2,5,1,3,4,3,3,6,4,4,8,3,3,6,32,42,74,'2025-11-06 02:35:13','2025-11-07 02:31:39'),(21,33,3,3,1,'2026-01-01 00:00:00','2026-03-27 00:00:00','ongoing','<p>Dalam menyusun laporan magang, bagian latar belakang sangat penting. Latar belakang ini menjelaskan alasan dan tujuan pelaksanaan magang, serta manfaat yang diperoleh. Beberapa hal yang perlu dicantumkan dalam latar belakang laporan magang adalahDalam menyusun laporan magang, bagian latar belakang sangat penting. Latar belakang ini menjelaskan alasan dan tujuan pelaksanaan magang, serta manfaat yang diperoleh. Beberapa hal yang perlu dicantumkan dalam latar belakang laporan magang adalahDalam menyusun laporan m