ta-start=\"1051\" data-end=\"1111\"><p data-start=\"1053\" data-end=\"1111\">Untuk <strong data-start=\"1059\" data-end=\"1070\">dokumen</strong>: gunakan <code data-start=\"1080\" data-end=\"1109\">name=\"dokumen_keterangan[]\"</code></p>\r\n</li><p>\r\n</p><li data-start=\"1112\" data-end=\"1166\">\r\n<p data-start=\"1114\" data-end=\"1166\"></p></li>','<p data-start=\"1168\" data-end=\"1206\">Contoh ubahan di <code data-start=\"1185\" data-end=\"1205\">_uploads.blade.php</code>:</p><p>\r\n</p><pre class=\"overflow-visible!\" data-start=\"1208\" data-end=\"3034\"><div class=\"contain-inline-size rounded-2xl relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary\"><div class=\"sticky top-9\"><div class=\"absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2\"><div class=\"bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary text-token-text-secondary flex items-center gap-4 rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs\"></div></div></div><div class=\"overflow-y-auto p-4\" dir=\"ltr\"></div></div></pre>','2025-11-06 02:16:38','2025-11-06 02:16:38');

