ity',NULL,NULL,NULL,'unset',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2025-06-30 20:30:54','2025-06-30 20:30:54'),(100,10,8,'App\\Models\\ProgramGoal','1','goal','Target\r\nTarget\r\nTarget\r\nAchievements\r\nAchievements\r\nAchievements',25,'75.00','to_be_conducted','Challenges\r\nChallenges\r\nChallenges\r\nChallenges','Mitigation / action plan\r\nMitigation / action plan\r\nMitigation / action plan','medium','Additionally, this tool is highly useful for generating data to fill spreadsheets, enabling you to test formulas, pivot tables, and data analysis functions with realistic datasets.','2025-12-24 00:26:45','2025-12-24 00:26:45'),(101,10,8,'App\\Models\\ProgramObjektif','1','objektif','Achievements\r\nAchievements\r\nAchievements',66,'34.00','completed','Practical Examples of Test Data Generation','Our test data generator simplifies the creation of dummy datasets. For example, if you need to test a form that collects user information, generate data that includes first names, last names, email addresses, and phone numbers.','high','Common Pitfalls When Using This Random Data Generator\r\nCommon Pitfalls When Using This Random Data Generator\r\nCommon Pitfalls When Using This Random Data Generator','2025-12-24 00:26:45','2025-12-24 00:26:45'),(102,10,1,'App\\Models\\Program_Outcome','1','outcome','Common Pitfalls When Using This Random Data Generator\r\nCommon Pitfalls When Using This Random Data Generator\r\nCommon Pitfalls When Using This Random Data Generator',96,'4.00','ongoing','Make sure you use plain simple language when describing your data needs. Plus, always review and test the generated datasets in real scenarios to ensure they function as intended. By providing these detailed sections on the landing page, potential users will have a clear understanding of the mock data generator\'s capabilities, usage, and practical applications, enhancing their experience and confidence in the tool.','While our random data generator is highly effective, it’s crucial to verify the data accuracy and relevance to your testing needs. Misconfigurations or overly broad input criteria can lead to data that doesn’t fully meet your requirements.','medium','To export the final output data, simply select the output data and copy it to your clipboard using the Command+C shortcut (or the Windows equivalent).','2025-12-24 00:26:45','2025-12-24 00:26:45'),(103,10,1,'App\\Models\\Program_Outcome_Output','1.1','output',NULL,NULL,NULL,'unset',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2025-12-24 00:26:45','2025-12-24 00:26:45'),(104,10,1,'App\\Models\\Program_Outcome_Output_Activity','1.1.1','activity',NULL,NULL,NULL,'unset',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2025-12-24 00:26:45','2025-12-24 00:26:45'),(105,10,2,'App\\Models\\Program_Outcome_Output_Activity','1.1.2','activity',NULL,NULL,NULL,'unset',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2025-12-24 00:26:45','2025-12-24 00:26:45'),(106,10,34,'App\\Models\\Program_Outcome_Output_Activity','1.1.3','activity',NULL,NULL,NULL,'unset',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2025-12-24 00:26:46','2025-12-24 00:26:46'),(107,10,34,'App\\Models\\Program_Outcome_Output_Activity','1.1.3','activity',NULL,NULL,NULL,'unset',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2025-12-24 00:26:46','2025-12-24 00:26:46'),(108,10,3,'App\\Models\\Program_Outcome_Output','1.2','output',NULL,NULL,NULL,'unset',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2025-12-24 00:26:46','2025-12-24 00:26:46'),(109,10,5,'App\\Models\\Program_Outcome_Output_Activity','1.2.1','activity',NULL,NULL,NULL,'unset',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2025-12-24 00:26:46','2025-12-24 00:26:46'),(110,10,2,'App\\Models\\Program_Outcome','2','outcome',NULL,NULL,NULL,'unset',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2025-12-24 00:26:46','2025-12-24 00:26:46'),(111,10,2,'App\\Models\\Program_Outcome_Output','2.1','output',NULL,NULL,NULL,'unset',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2025-12-24 00:26:46','2025-12-24 00:26:46'),(112,10,3,'App\\Models\\Program_Outcome_Output_Activity','2.1.1','activity',NULL,NULL,NULL,'unset',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2025-12-24 00:26:46','2025-12-24 00:26:46'),(113,10,4,'App\\Models\\Program_Outcome_Output_Activity',