insert  into `trprogram`(`id`,`nama`,`kode`,`tanggalmulai`,`tanggalselesai`,`totalnilai`,`ekspektasipenerimamanfaat`,`ekspektasipenerimamanfaatwoman`,`ekspektasipenerimamanfaatman`,`ekspektasipenerimamanfaatgirl`,`ekspektasipenerimamanfaatboy`,`ekspektasipenerimamanfaattidaklangsung`,`deskripsiprojek`,`analisamasalah`,`user_id`,`status`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (1,'PROGRAM-1','#PR-1','2024-10-31 00:00:00','2024-12-30 00:00:00','100000000000.00',809,111,122,231,222,123,'Mock data is crucial for a variety of development and testing scenarios. Use it to populate databases, simulate API responses, or create realistic test cases for web applications.\r\n\r\nWhether you’re stress-testing a system with large volumes of data or verifying the functionality of specific features under different conditions, random data ensures thorough and efficient testing.','Our test data generator simplifies the creation of dummy datasets. For example, if you need to test a form that collects user information, generate data that includes first names, last names, email addresses, and phone numbers.',1,'submit','2024-10-31 22:27:28','2025-12-24 00:22:52'),(2,'Community-based Food Forest for Climate Justice Model in North Bali (Phase 2)','#PR-2','2023-07-01 00:00:00','2025-06-30 00:00:00','2024.00',137,9,21,0,0,107,'Climate change is a global phenomenon that significantly impacts the environment,\r\neconomy, and society. Agriculture is one of the sectors most affected by climate change, with\r\nthe changing weather patterns, increasing temperatures, and extreme weather events\r\naffecting crop yields, water availability, and livestock production. These impacts\r\ndisproportionately affect smallholder farmers in developing countries, who often lack the\r\nresources and knowledge to adapt to the changing climate.','As a biodiversity hotspot, Indonesia’s vast tropical forests and marine habitats provide many\r\necosystem services, such as clean air and water and flood control. However, Indonesia’s\r\neconomic growth over the past two decades has accelerated urbanization and the expansion\r\nof agricultural land use to serve growing domestic and international commodity markets. This\r\ngrowth has challenged sustainable resource management and made',1,'complete','2024-11-06 03:17:28','2025-09-18 21:40:49'),(3,'DREAMS Project : Disaster Resilience through Education, Adaptation, and Mitigation Strategies','#PR-3-UPDATED','2024-02-01 00:00:00','2024-08-31 00:00:00','2024.00',360,18,42,0,0,300,'This is a 6-month project with the summary of activities as follows:\r\nCapacity building on Disaster Risk Reduction and Climate Adaptation and Mitigation, both in targeted villages and schools, through assessments, training and workshops, the establishment of Community Disaster Management Group (KMPB), and development of disaster risk mapping and anticipatory action plan.\r\nDisaster risk management systems establishment through Table Top Exercises and disaster drills based on the communities’ risk','Climate change has significantly increased the frequency of hydrometeorological disasters in various regions of Indonesia, including the villages of Waimatan and Banyu Biru. The tropical cyclone Seroja and the flash flood in April 2021 resulted in damage to infrastructure, loss of lives, disruption of access to necessities, and the disruption of livelihoods. 26 people have died and 8 other victims have not been found until today, while 29 houses were damaged by the flash flood. The disasters als',1,'running','2024-11-15 11:24:44','2025-12-23 00:37:44'),(4,'PROGRAM 4 - PAKAI TEST INI','#PR-4','2025-12-22 00:00:00','2026-12-22 00:00:00','900000000.00',25,5,5,5,5,5,'This Deskripsi Program','Analisis Masalah Program',1,'submit','2024-12-06 18:20:51','2025-12-22 23:56:54'),(5,'PROGRAM 5 - PAKAI TEST INI ','#PR-5','2024-12-06 00:00:00','2024-12-07 00:00:00','900000000.00',125,25,25,25,25,25,'This is Description of Program','This is Analisis of program',2,'draft','2024-12-06 18:44:09','2024-12-11 23:30:42'),(7,'PROGRAM XX','PR-XX','2025-02-05 00:00:00','2025-02-28 00:00:00','192.00',80,12,12,21,23,12,'Deskripsi','Analisis',1,'draft','2025-02-05 01:55:33','2025-11-07 02:29:14'),(8,'Program Action Test Developers','#01012026','2025-01-02 00:00:00','2026-01-02 00:00:00','1000000000.00',45,9,9,9,9,9,'Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat. Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate velit esse cillum dolore eu fugiat nulla pariatur. Excepteur sint occaecat cupidatat non proident, sunt in culpa qui officia deserunt mollit anim id est laborum.','Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat. Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate velit esse cillum dolore eu fugiat nulla pariatur. Excepteur sint occaecat cupidatat non proident, sunt in culpa qui officia deserunt mollit anim id est laborum.',1,'running','2025-06-19 23:16:44','2026-01-02 00:43:25'),(9,'Dummy Program','#PR-20','2025-06-20 00:00:00','2025-06-27 00:00:00','1000000000.00',1000,200,500,100,100,100,'Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat. Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate velit esse cillum dolore eu fugiat nulla pariatur. Excepteur sint occaecat cupidatat non proident, sunt in culpa qui officia deserunt mollit anim id est laborum.','Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat. Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate velit esse cillum dolore eu fugiat nulla pariatur. Excepteur sint occaecat cupidatat non proident, sunt in culpa qui officia deserunt mollit anim id est laborum.',1,'draft','2025-06-20 18:14:44','2025-06-20 18:14:44'),(14,'Program XXX','#PR-XXX','2025-06-30 00:00:00','2025-07-05 00:00:00','100000000.00',10,10,10,10,10,10,'Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry.','Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry.',1,'draft','2025-06-30 19:48:23','2025-06-30 19:49:37'),(15,'MU Juara Liga Inggris','#MU VS ARSENAL','2025-08-01 00:00:00','2025-10-31 00:00:00','2999999999.00',73,20,20,11,11,11,'MU Juara Liga Inggris\r\n\r\nManchester United selalu saja dipenuhi masalah setiap memulai musim. Meski diarsiteki Erik Ten Hag yang membuat impresi di musim pertamanya dengan MU, tapi Setan Merah tetap belum meyakinkan.','Dia melihat MU tak punya peluang untuk menyaingi Manchester city dalam perebutan juara. Dia menilai hanya Liverpool dan Arsenal yang bisa mengimbangi Man City musim ini.\r\n\r\n\"Liverpool dan Arsenal menjadi dua pesaing terakhir bagi Manchester City musim ini,\" kata Merson seperti dikutip Sky sport.\r\n\r\nPendapat ini dikatakannya karena melihat MU tak bisa tampil seperti Liverpool dan Arsenal. Dimana dua klub yang disebut terakhir selalu bisa keluar dari tekanan setiap kali tertinggal dari lawan.',1,'draft','2025-08-20 23:45:22','2025-08-20 23:45:22'),(16,'Reds Utd','#123','2025-09-01 00:00:00','2025-10-11 00:00:00','190000000000.00',281,12,12,12,22,223,NULL,NULL,1,'submit','2025-09-08 01:40:47','2025-09-08 01:54:11'),(17,'Play Fantasy Premier League','#FPL','2025-12-01 00:00:00','2026-10-16 00:00:00','9000.00',105,1,1,2,2,99,'With over 11 million players, Fantasy Premier League is the biggest Fantasy Football game in the world. It\'s FREE to play and you can win great prizes!','See which players are missing from every team, with our injury list guide to all 20 clubs and FPL team news\r\n\r\nSee all the players injured for each of the 20 Premier League clubs, with key news for managers in Fantasy Premier League.',1,'draft','2025-09-16 01:50:12','2025-09-16 01:50:41');

